hyperplane `S' ‚äā S‚āÄ` of dimension `s - 1` is not covering (used in proof
of part (a)). This is a direct consequence of minimality. -/
lemma not_covering_of_lt_minimal {m p : ‚Ąē}
    (S‚āÄ S' : Submodule ‚ĄĚ (Matrix (Fin m) (Fin p) ‚ĄĚ))
    (hS‚āÄ : IsMinimalCovering S‚āÄ)
    (hS'lt : S' < S‚āÄ) :
    ¬¨ IsCovering S' := by
  intro hcov
  exact hS‚āÄ.2 S' (le_of_lt hS'lt) (ne_of_lt hS'lt) hcov

snip end

